                {
                  "speaker": "Reinn",
                  "text": "Good day, traveller."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "And to you."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "After completing The Fremennik Trials",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Reinn",
                  "text": "Good to see you, [Fremennik name]!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hello there. You're a long way from home."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Reinn",
                  "text": "Well what sort of Fremennik are you if you don't travel! Besides, we heard this was the land to visit for breaking skulls and spilling blood!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Is it?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Reinn",
                  "text": "Of course! Have you not visited the Colosseum? You won't regret it if you do."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hmm... I might have to check it out."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Reinn",
                  "text": "Ha! As if you didn't know! We've heard about your exploits in the Colosseum! Maybe you'll see us next time you're there!"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "dialogues": []
    }
